snippet.textDisplay:
05:13 Can't explain my love, pride and excitement ❤️ CS Pakistan just keeps stealing my heart 🥺 Here's a Tunisian who adores Pakistani music so I'm so proud and glad to see Sidi Mansour, our traditional Nouba, being revisited by Karpe and I'm so in love with Piya Piya Calling 🌌✨just brilliant ! Immense thanks for bringing them and all these cultures together 🤍
*A Nouba or Hadhra  is a Tunisian type of songs that pays a tribute and praises a wali (a pious and truly spiritual personality).. AP ye samjhe it's kinda the Qawwali equivalent♡
